{
  "stem": "5891.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then when we got older and we were traveling, my dad and my mom in the front there, like you could see there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were sat in the back there, between-- it's like a connection.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a connection there between the wagon and that trailer, that little trailer there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not that little.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to sit here and used to sing all the way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Harmony from the first to the second-- the four-- we were four sisters about the same age there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to sing good harmony together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then my dad used to say-- he would sometimes command it if he got together with his friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I want you to listen to my daughters, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were sitting there, and we had to sing there, harmonize one German song after another, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this-- this is just little excitement, what I told you about, growing up with those type of wonderful, wonderful things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Wonderful, wonderful things.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you only have those lifetimes once, and you don't ever get that chance again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's why I said you should enjoy your growth, all your growing up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I tell my children that it goes by so fast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What language did you speak in your family?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We speak German, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we also speak-- if you were in with the other people, they speak like a Romani's language, OK?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that we speak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we spoke that with the old folks who didn't speak English-- German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They spoke with that-- that Romanis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, if I wanted to talk about somebody, if we girls wanted to talk about somebody, we'd talk the Romanis.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do it today with my children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My children learned.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
